Manufacturer Dashboard - Complete Feature Goals
1. School Management
View all registered schools (active, pending, suspended)
Search and filter schools by name, status, location, subscription plan
View detailed school information (contact, subscription, usage stats)
Suspend/unsuspend schools
Delete schools (with confirmation)
Export school list to CSV/Excel
2. Registration Approval System
View pending school registrations in Excel-style table
Review detailed registration information
Approve registrations (creates school account + admin user)
Reject registrations with reason
View registration history (approved/rejected)
Bulk approve/reject multiple registrations
3. Subscription Management
View all active subscriptions
See subscription plans (Essential, Professional, Enterprise, Premium)
Monitor subscription expiration dates
Manually upgrade/downgrade school plans
Extend trial periods
View subscription revenue analytics
4. Payment Tracking
View all payments (completed, pending, failed)
Track payment history per school
Generate payment reports
View revenue analytics (daily, monthly, yearly)
Export payment data
5. User Management
View all users across all schools
Search users by name, email, role, school
View user activity logs
Manually reset user passwords
Suspend/activate user accounts
View login history and security events
6. Analytics & Reporting
Dashboard overview with key metrics:
Total schools (active/pending/suspended)
Total users by role
Total revenue (monthly/yearly)
Active subscriptions by plan
Student count across platform
Growth charts (schools, users, revenue over time)
Usage statistics per school
Export reports to PDF/Excel
7. Platform Configuration
Manage subscription plans and pricing
Configure platform-wide settings
Set trial period duration
Configure email templates
Manage feature flags per plan
8. Communication Tools
Send announcements to all schools
Send targeted emails to specific schools
View communication history
Create email templates
9. Support & Bug Tracking
View bug reports from schools
Assign priority levels
Track bug status (open, in progress, resolved)
Respond to bug reports
View support tickets
10. Security & Audit
View audit logs (all platform actions)
Monitor failed login attempts
View security events
Track data access logs
Export audit reports
11. Billing Management
Generate invoices for schools
Track outstanding payments
Send payment reminders
Apply discounts/coupons
Manage refunds
12. School Onboarding
View onboarding progress per school
Send onboarding guides
Track feature adoption
Provide setup assistance
13. Data Management
Backup database
Export platform data
View storage usage per school
Manage data retention policies
14. Notifications
Real-time notifications for:
New school registrations
Payment failures
Critical bugs
Subscription expirations
Security alerts
15. Profile & Settings
Update manufacturer profile
Change password
Enable 2FA
Set notification preferences
View session history